{"lemma":"مُقَرَّبٌ","slug":"مُقَرَّبٌ","root":"ق.ر.ب","root_slug":"ق-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ب","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُقَرَّب","root":"قرب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":8},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35417","n35418","n35419"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A8%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35417","headword_ar":"مَقْرَبٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqorabapN","text_ar":"مَقْرَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearest, road"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small road"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way, leading into a great one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqarabu","text_ar":"القَرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the journeying by night, ” or “ the journeying [by night] to water: ” (TA:) or, the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a conspicuous road"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says IAar: (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTorabN","text_ar":"مَطْرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and the latter, accord. to AA,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of alighting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sojourning"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abiding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqarabu","text_ar":"القَرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the ” journeying [by night &c.]: the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqaAribu","text_ar":"مَقَارِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2509}],"source_refs":["A","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n35418","headword_ar":"مُقْرَبٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is brought"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kept"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the tent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dwelling"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and treated generously, and not left to seek for pasture:"},{"kind":"text","text":"fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or this is done only with mares, lest a stallion of low race should cover them: (IDrd, S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayolN muqorabapN","text_ar":"خَيْلٌ مُقْرَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horses that are"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kept"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near at hand, and prepared"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for riding"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (El-Ahmar, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horses that have been prepared by scant food"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dum~irato","text_ar":"ضُمِّرَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for riding:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horses of generous race, that are not confined in the pasturage, but are confined near to the tents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dwellings, prepared for running."},{"kind":"text","text":"(R, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibilN muqorabapN","text_ar":"اـِبِلٌ مُقْرَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Camels girded for riding:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels upon which are saddles"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHaAl","text_ar":"رِحَال"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cased with leather, whereon kings ride:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this explanation has been disallowed. (Aboo-Sa'eed [i. e. As], TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mukorabaAtN","text_ar":"مُكْرَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["IDrd","S","O","K","Sh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n35419","headword_ar":"مُقْرِبٌ","root":"qrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A woman, and a mare, and a ewe or goat, (S, O,) and an ass, (Lth, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near to bringing forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA:) [said to be] not used in relation to a camel; (S, O, TA;) the epithet used in this case being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudonK","text_ar":"مُدْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [but see the verb:] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqaAriybu","text_ar":"مَقَارِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K, TA;) as though they had imagined the sing. to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqoraAbN","text_ar":"مِقْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Lth","TA","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}